# Content Update Rules

## The Golden Rule
**All content changes go to `src/config/site.config.ts` only.**

## Sections and Their Config Keys

| Page / Section  | Config key              |
|-----------------|-------------------------|
| Header logo     | `company.logoText`      |
| Hero headline   | `hero.headline`         |
| Hero stats      | `hero.stats[]`          |
| About           | `about.summary/mission/vision/highlights` |
| Solutions       | `solutions[]`           |
| Tech Stack      | `techStack[]`           |
| Services        | `services[]`            |
| Products        | `products[]`            |
| Careers         | `careers.positions[]`   |
| Partners        | `partners.categories[]` |
| Clients list    | `clients[]`             |
| News            | `news[]`                |
| Events          | `events[]`              |
| Contact details | `company.contact`       |
| SEO metadata    | `seo`                   |
| Navigation      | `navigation[]`          |
| Chat assistant | `chatbot` (welcome, suggestions, `faqs[]` with `keywords` + `answer`) |

## Adding a New Service
```ts
{
  id: "unique-id",          // used for anchor links /services#unique-id
  title: "Service Name",
  icon: "IconName",         // must exist in src/components/ui/IconResolver.tsx
  summary: "One line.",
  description: "Full paragraph.",
  technologies: ["Tech1", "Tech2"],  // optional
}
```

## Adding a New Tech Category
```ts
{
  category: "Category Name",
  icon: "IconName",
  color: "from-blue-500/20 to-cyan-500/20",
  technologies: ["Item 1", "Item 2"],
}
```

## Changing the Company
Replace ALL values in the `company` block:
- `name`, `shortName`, `logoText`, `tagline`, `description`
- `contact.address`, `contact.phone`, `contact.emails`
- `seo.title`, `seo.description`

That's it — no component changes needed.
